{"tid":2235400,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳C朗7層高大宅遭匪徒爆竊","createTime":"2020-10-08T15:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T03:09:04.000Z","uid":138707,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3fdc85b83bbfd15880be83f69972a9daff362255","tid":2235400,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度位於葡萄牙的大宅遭匪徒爆竊，當地警方正在調查事件，財物損失仍在點算當中。<br />\n葡萄牙傳媒《Diario de Noticias Madeira》報道，一名匪徒周三早上潛入了基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）位於葡萄牙馬德拉的7層高大宅進行爆竊，消息指，該匪徒是從大宅一個打開了的車庫門進入屋內行事，暫未知總失損失多少財物，但據知當中包括1件有C朗親筆簽名的祖雲達斯球衣。 葡萄牙警方事後已到大宅作初步調查，並已從閉路電視片段中鎖定匪徒的身份，但現階段仍未有任何人被捕。 英國《每日郵報》指，C朗母親Dolores Aviero仍是居住在這幢7層高大宅，事發時是否在場不得而知。新冠疫情初期，C朗跟女友洛迪古絲和他的孩子都是在這幢大宅的最高兩層樓避疫，之後才遷往距離半小時車程的一間別墅居住。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E5%82%B3c%E6%9C%977%E5%B1%A4%E9%AB%98%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%85%E9%81%AD%E5%8C%AA%E5%BE%92%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A-132226663.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%2582%25B3c%25E6%259C%25977%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%2585%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258C%25AA%25E5%25BE%2592%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258A-132226663.html&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=6a32a92f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E5%82%B3c%E6%9C%977%E5%B1%A4%E9%AB%98%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%85%E9%81%AD%E5%8C%AA%E5%BE%92%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A-132226663.html</a>"},{"pid":"92d3f79a9ce87441a829f8f1852a0f942af6ee1e","tid":2235400,"uid":176282,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"打開夾萬發現全部係雞胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e39fa03f25b7a40c06de784e7d7ec3d8229009","tid":2235400,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92d3f79a9ce87441a829f8f1852a0f942af6ee1e","tid":2235400,"uid":176282,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"打開夾萬發現全部係雞胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi